// PSP macros for MOSVAR surface potential model
// Version 1.3.0-beta, March 2015
//
// Note: This file contains macro definitions for the PSP model used in MOSVAR.
// It is an include file, not a standalone module.
// Cannot be directly translated to PHDL as it contains no module.

/*
This file contains macro definitions for PSP model quantities:
- Mathematical constants (X1, invSqrt2, P3(u), sqt_exp)
- Exponential function macros (expl, expl_low, expl_high)
- sigma function macro for surface potential calculations
- Various other computational macros

This is an include file, not a standalone module.
To use these macros, they would need to be converted to PHDL functions/constants.
*/